com.googlecode.objectify.impl.ref

Class ProxyRef<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.objectify.Ref<T>
      • com.googlecode.objectify.impl.ref.ProxyRef<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Ref<T>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FirstRef

    public abstract class ProxyRef<T>
extends Ref<T>

    An implementation of Ref that works like a proxy. We can't create dynamic proxies on abstract classes and we don't want to suck in a bytecode manipulator dependency so we have to create this by hand. No big deal.

    Author:
    Jeff Schnitzer
